        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Chesapeake Bay Science, Education, and Ecosystem Enhancement Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill reauthorizes through FY2025 the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's Chesapeake Bay Office and revises requirements concerning the office and its activities. It also authorizes the office to establish a Chesapeake Bay watershed education and training program as well as a program to support coordinated management, protection, characterization, and restoration of priority habitats and living resources.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
